org.eclipse.dataset.metadata

Interface IMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, IDataAnalysisObject, MetadataType, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IExtendedMetadata
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Metadata

    public interface IMetadata
extends IDataAnalysisObject, MetadataType, java.io.Serializable
    This interface describes the minimal metadata information that should be associated with a Dataset or DataHolder. It is intended that this interface will be implemented in an object that will then be associated with a DataHolder or dataset using setMetadata(IMetadata).

    All returned collections and maps are unmodifiable.
